@startuml
title Viaverse Phase / Task / Release State — State Diagram

[*] --> IDEA
IDEA --> PLANNED : accepted
PLANNED --> READY : scope + acceptance
READY --> IN_PROGRESS : start
IN_PROGRESS --> BLOCKED : dependency/risk
BLOCKED --> IN_PROGRESS : unblocked
IN_PROGRESS --> IN_REVIEW : PR/test
IN_REVIEW --> IN_PROGRESS : changes
IN_REVIEW --> DONE : approved
DONE --> RELEASED : release train
RELEASED --> HOTFIX_REQUIRED : incident/regression
HOTFIX_REQUIRED --> IN_PROGRESS : fix branch
PLANNED --> SUPERSEDED : strategy changed

RELEASED --> [*]
SUPERSEDED --> [*]

note bottom
A task cannot move to DONE without tests/docs where applicable.
A phase cannot move to RELEASED without release gate signoff and rollback path.
end note
@enduml
